Looks up a localized string similar to Syntax: UUEncode /? | [/e | /d] inFilename outFilename
Switches: /? Displays this help. /e Encode a file (the default) /d Decode a file /s:<size> Encode/decode in <size> blocks. Parameters: inFileName The file to be encoded/decoded. outFilename The encoded/decoded file to be created. .
